metadata.title: DPM Dar, Egyptian FM discuss ME, Gaza situation

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Oct 11 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar and Egyptian Foreign Minister Dr. Badr Abdelatty on Saturday exchanged views on the ongoing situation in the Middle East, particularly the developments in Gaza and Palestine. Deputy Prime Minister and Foreign Minister Dar spoke with the Egyptian foreign minister, Foreign Office Spokesperson said in a press release. They also discussed regional diplomatic efforts and coordination ahead of the forthcoming Summit scheduled to take place in Sharm el-Sheikh on Monday.
